text: The Laval Associés () is Laval's baseball team in the Ligue de Baseball Élite du Québec. They play at Montmorency Park in the Laval-des-Rapides neighbourhood. ==Former players== *Jonathan Malo, New York Mets farm system ==External links== * Team website Category:Baseball teams in Quebec Category:Sport in Laval, Quebec Category:1983 establishments in Quebec Category:Baseball teams established in 1983
